- mutex group endpoints
- experiment traffic allocation
- bucketing configuration
- slot management
- evaluation mode (local/remote)
- bucketing key and salt
- traffic percentage distribution
- experiment slot assignment
- holdout group integration
- individual user targeting
- cohort assignment
- mutex group archiving
- experiment mutual exclusion